column6: " PART 3- THE GRAND FINALE OF INHUMAN ERROR"! - Red Raven has Spider-Man and the Inhumans right where he wants them! - One bird turn deserves another, as the All-New Captain America answers the call to defend New York from the revenge-ready Red Raven!
column8: | penciller (cover):Jamal Campbell | writer:Jeff Loveness | artist:Alec Morgan
